quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  42,52,"Likewise, We have revealed to you a revelation by Our command. You knew nothing of the Scripture or matters of faith, but We have made it [i.e., the Qur’an] a light by which We guide whom We will of Our slaves. And you are truly leading people to a straight path,",""
  42,53,"the path of Allah, to Whom belongs all that is in the heavens and all that is on earth. Indeed, to Allah return all matters.",""
  43,1,"Hā Mīm<sup>1</sup>.","[1] See footnote 2:1."
  43,2,"By the clear Book,",""
  43,3,"Indeed, We have made it an Arabic Qur’an so that you may understand,",""
  43,4,"and it is in the Master Book<sup>2</sup> with us, highly esteemed, full of wisdom.","[2] i.e., the Preserved Tablet (al-Lawh al-Mahfūz)."
  43,5,"Should We then turn the Reminder<sup>3</sup> away from you simply because you are a transgressing people?","[3] i.e., the Qur’an."
  43,6,"How many a prophet did We send to the earlier peoples!",""
  43,7,"No prophet ever came to them except that they ridiculed him.",""
  43,8,"So We destroyed them, although they were greater in might than these [Pagans]<sup>4</sup>, and the stories of the earlier nations have already been related<sup>5</sup>.","[4] Of the Quraysh.\n [5] Such as the people of Noah, Lot, Shu’ayb and other nations who were destroyed."
  43,9,"If you ask them, “Who created the heavens and earth?”, they will surely say, “The All-Mighty, the All-Knowing created them.”",""
  43,10,"It is He Who spread out the earth for you, and made therein pathways for you, so that you may find your way.",""
